signupStep0Explanation: Faka ikheli lakho le-imeyili ukuze udale i-akhawunti yakho. Ungakwazi futhi ukusebenzisa ukungena ngemvume kwe-Google ukuze uthole ukufinyelela okusheshayo.
signupStep1Explanation: Khetha igama lakho lokubonisa. Lena yindlela abanye abasebenzisi abazokubona ngayo ku-uChat.
signupStep2Explanation: Ithegi yakho yegama lomsebenzisi iqala ngokuthi @ uphawu. Lesi sikhombi esiyingqayizivele sisiza abanye ukuthi bakuthole. Akekho omunye umsebenzisi ongaba nomaka ofanayo.
signupStep3Explanation: Dala iphasiwedi eqinile ukuze uvikele i-akhawunti yakho.
signupStep4Explanation: Qinisekisa iphasiwedi yakho futhi wamukele imigomo ukuze uqedele ukubhalisa.
